{"tid":262606,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【劏場哀歌】大日子商場劈價三成沽貨尾 業主即時坐艇","createTime":"2017-05-29T10:58:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T23:34:14.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a1f645f6f978cf87dad1c9c8d3568b2b9b47d82e","tid":262606,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T10:58:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170529/large/1496053248_c85a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170529%2Flarge%2F1496053248_c85a.jpg&h=e971e811&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大日子商場兩年前拆售，以140萬元入場，結果短時間內沽出大部份舖位。(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n樓價一直急升，惟獨劏場獨憔悴，先後出現多宗大幅蝕讓。在兩年前拆售的大埔大日子商場，開售至今未有錄得任何二手成交，不過大業主新近售出2樓一個撻定貨，竟較兩年前低三成的152萬元重售，意味商場其他業主即時坐艇。<br />\n<br />\n大埔鄉事會街9至15號寶蓮樓大日子商場2樓240號舖，建築面積66方呎，原本於2015年7月以219.78萬元售出，呎價3.33萬元。但有關交易在去年中取消。根據土地註冊處資料顯示，該舖剛以152萬元重售，較兩年前一手價勁跌67.78萬元，呎價急挫30.8%至2.3萬元，成為商場最平呎價舖位。<br />\n<br />\n大日子商場由「劏場大王」尹柏權在2015年6月拆售，三層共220個舖位，入場費約140萬元起，由於提供首兩年5厘租金回報保證，結果短時間內沽出大部份舖位。雖然去年曾有個別舖位撻定，但都能以原價重售，惟獨最新的240號舖要以低價售出，令一直未有二手成交的商場，業主更難望以高於購入價出售舖位。<br />\n<br />\n由於現時業主仍收取租金回報，市場未有成交，而商場2樓260號舖，面積56方呎，今年3月曾以開價170萬元推出拍賣，已平過購入價59.1萬元或26%，可惜未能人承價收回。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56758259&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170529\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56758259%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170529&d=JusVMO8o1agBzVcejjMw%2B6EKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=14264490\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56758259%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170529&h=0e8f1ff5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56758259&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170529</a>"},{"pid":"9c12a917ace9ee350d3984fc5b78cfb119d30e2f","tid":262606,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T11:04:34.000Z","msg":"點解會有人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"884052797292799519b4bc3a7b603cea79860825","tid":262606,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T11:08:39.000Z","msg":"呢個場係死城黎 明明附近人流好多 近街市 <br />\n但硬係就無人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f4f1271ba6c3178e810f7e42a4b86edd31493d","tid":262606,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T11:10:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解會有人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我師父沈大師講過，太平山下老襯多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n劏場全香港95%輸錢嘅，唔熟唔好玩，魔鬼在細節，管理公司通常大莊打龍通 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fe85e88240266a6b3fd3a22b5f4015ae7f6ba86","tid":262606,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T11:19:33.000Z","msg":"都係果句，個場有得做既話點解大業主唔做要拆細賣俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded832156c925144cf0bd2c0964a00287fedc22d","tid":262606,"uid":47160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T11:28:42.000Z","msg":"住附近只係上過去一次，間舖細過我屋企廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n心諗轉做wargame場把啦"},{"pid":"7d8a480bc8f8ba0d33b8fc0e79f17a006fdaf4a6","tid":262606,"uid":77542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T